</style> <section class="max-w-page mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-8" id="what-is"> <h2 class="f-meta-mono mb-6">What is Fontelio</h2> <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4"> <div class="f-capsule"> <div class="f-capsule-eyebrow">01 / Subsets</div> <h3 class="f-capsule-title">WOFF2 subsets, only what you need</h3> <p class="f-capsule-body">Latin, Cyrillic, Greek, Vietnamese — picked per family, served as separate woff2 files with proper unicode-range so the browser only downloads what the page renders.</p> </div><div class="f-capsule"> <div class="f-capsule-eyebrow">02 / Bundles</div> <h3 class="f-capsule-title">On-the-fly ZIP bundles</h3> <p class="f-capsule-body">Pick the weights and styles you want, get a single download. Useful for design handoff, branding kits, or seeding another self-hosted install.</p> </div><div class="f-capsule"> <div class="f-capsule-eyebrow">03 / Privacy</div> <h3 class="f-capsule-title">GDPR-friendly by default</h3> <p class="f-capsule-body">Every font is served from your own infrastructure — no third-party requests, no tracking, no analytics calls leaking visitor IPs. A drop-in replacement for Google Fonts that keeps your visitors&#39; data on your domain.</p> </div> </div> </section> <section class="max-w-page mx-auto px-6 pt-8 pb-16" id="docs"> <h2 class="f-meta-mono mb-6">Embed in two lines</h2> <div class="f-embed"> <button type="button" class="f-embed-copy" id="f-copy" data-text="<link rel=&#34;stylesheet&#34; href=&#34;https://www.fontelio.com/css2?family=!CRASS+ROOTS+Alt:wght@400&#38;display=swap&#34;>

body { font-family: '!CRASS ROOTS Alt', sans-serif; }" data-copy-label="Copy" data-copied-label="Copied">Copy</button> <code>&lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;https://www.fontelio.com/css2?family=!CRASS+ROOTS+Alt:wght@400&amp;display=swap&quot;&gt;

body { font-family: &#39;!CRASS ROOTS Alt&#39;, sans-serif; }</code> </div> <p class="text-muted text-sm mt-3">The /css2 endpoint mirrors the Google Fonts API. Swap the family name and weights to taste.</p> </section> <footer class="f-footer"> <div class="max-w-page mx-auto px-6"> <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-8"> <div> <a class="f-brand mb-3 inline-flex" href="/"> <span class="f-brand-f">F</span><span class="f-brand-rest">ontelio</span> </a> <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed mt-2 max-w-xs"> Self-hosted Google Fonts alternative — privacy-first, edge-delivered. </p> </div> <div> <h4 class="f-meta-mono mb-3">Catalog</h4> <ul class="space-y-2"> <li> <a href="/fonts/" class="text-sm text-ink hover:text-accent transition-colors">Browse all</a> </li><li> <a href="/font-type/sans-serif/" class="text-sm text-ink hover:text-accent transition-colors">Sans-serif</a> </li><li> <a href="/font-type/serif/" class="text-sm text-ink hover:text-accent transition-colors">Serif</a> </li><li> <a href="/font-type/monospace/" class="text-sm text-ink hover:text-accent transition-colors">Monospace</a> </li><li> <a href="/designers/" class="text-sm text-ink hover:text-accent transition-colors">Designers</a> </li> </ul> </div><div> <h4 class="f-meta-mono mb-3">Company</h4> <ul class="space-y-2"> <li> <a href="/about/" class="text-sm text-ink hover:text-accent transition-colors">About</a> </li><li> <a href="/blog/" class="text-sm text-ink hover:text-accent transition-colors">Blog</a> </li><li> <a href="/terms/" class="text-sm text-ink hover:text-accent transition-colors">Terms</a> </li><li> <a href="/privacy/" class="text-sm text-ink hover:text-accent transition-colors">Privacy</a> </li> </ul> </div> </div> <div class="mb-8"><div class="f-lang" role="group" aria-label="Language"> <span class="f-lang-link is-active" aria-current="true"> <img src="/_assets-static/flag-en.svg" alt="" width="16" height="12"> <span>EN</span> </span><a class="f-lang-link" href="/pt/